short_summary: FCC requires the storage and shipment  services that are currently being provided. We would like to find one  Proponent to meet all the needs that we have, however we are open to multiple Proponents in regards to: Storage of all marketing and promotional items and material, Storage of additional items such as moving bins, seasonal items, etc., Ability to  ship all requested items as needed, Ability to handle all mailouts as requested, etc.
